required software:

- scons
- libglew1.5-dev
- llvm2.8
- packetizer
- ATI Stream SDK v2.1

installation:

- build llvm
- build packetizer
- install stream sdk
	- place ICD registration config files in /etc/OpenCL/vendors or use christophs hack :p
	- set ATISTREAMSDKROOT and ATISTREAMSDKSAMPLESROOT environment variables to stream sdk root dir
	- build stream sdk (ignore errors related to CAL)
- adjust 'setupenv.sh' and/or 'setupenvdebug.sh' to match your system (for llvm2.8 currently setupenvlatest/setupenvlatestdebug)
- source 'setupenv.sh' or 'setupenvdebug.sh' to build in opt or debug mode
- run scons, options (default shown):
	debug=0
	debug-runtime=0
	profile=0
	packetize=0 (enable packetization)
	openmp=0 (enable openmp multi threading (4 threads))
	split=0  (disable mem access optimizations)
	static=0 (build static driver library instead of shared)
